    <cas:Sofa xmi:id="1" sofaNum="1" sofaID="_InitialView" mimeType="text" sofaString="[21-27 June 2021, Cox's Bazar] Community-based Mortality surveillance: • In week 25, 36 deaths were recorded - • 64% (n=23) were due to causes classified as “Others” • 8% (n=3) as still birth (Born Dead) • 16% (n=6) as neonatal (&lt;28 days old) • 3% (n=1) as infectious disease • 6% (n=2) as maternal death • 3% (n=1) as severe acute respiratory infection (SARI) • Out of reported deaths, 25% occurred in health facilities and 75% at homes. • Partners to report all mortalities into EWARS platform using both case and event-based reporting as applicable."/>
